props.name: color
props.description: Background color of component. Functional colors such as `info`, `success`, `warning` and `error` add a default icon on the left.

props.name: showIcon
props.description: Show an icon defaulted to the functional colors, e.g. `info`, `success`, `warning` and `error`.

props.name: class
props.description: A space-separated list of the classes of the element.

props.name: screen
props.description: Responsive properties based on minimum screen widths.
